OL,3,CAre you set to benefit from the
OL,4,CChancellor's National Insurance cut?
OL,6,FThe change will take effect from this
OL,7,FApril, at the start of the new tax
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FIt's a UK-wide tax, so applies across
OL,11,Fall four nations.
OL,13,FWho does it apply to?
OL,15,FIt only applies to earned income, so
OL,16,Fpensioners won't be impacted, nor will
OL,17,Fthose who receive income from savings
OL,18,Fand investments such as property.
